article.headline: UC Riverside 75, UC Irvine 66
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- Phil Martin scored 21 points and UC Riverside defeated UC Irvine 75-66 on Saturday night. Martin made 8 of 14 shots for the Highlanders (11-18, 6-10), who also got 11 points each from B.J. Shearry and Kareem Nitoto. Eric Wise scored 20 points and Darren Moore added 14 for the Anteaters (13-18, 6-10 Big West), who trailed 43-31 at halftime. UC Riverside made 29 of 60 shots while UC Irvine connected on 23 of 60. The Highlanders controlled the boards, outrebounding the Anteaters 44-32 as Shearry had nine.
